WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.769 --> 00:00:04.770
JOHN OLIVER:<i> Crime.</i>

00:00:04.870 --> 00:00:06.472
You know that thing that was
almost solved

00:00:06.572 --> 00:00:08.908
-by a flasher dog in 1980's.
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

