But specifically this story
is about

00:00:10.576 --> 00:00:13.413
how we increasingly solve crimes
using forensic evidence.

00:00:13.513 --> 00:00:15.648
It's that thing that
is just a staple

00:00:15.748 --> 00:00:17.116
of TV crime shows.

00:00:17.650 --> 00:00:20.486
Pull it from the torso
on the left.

00:00:20.953 --> 00:00:22.789
Pull it from
the boat on the right.

