had already been executed,

00:04:59.365 --> 00:05:01.400
-(AUDIENCE SWOONING)
-which is horrifying.

00:05:01.500 --> 00:05:04.804
And you would expect
FBI hair analysis

00:05:04.904 --> 00:05:08.174
to have a high rate of accuracy
than your friend's hair analysis

00:05:08.274 --> 00:05:10.576
of you can
totally pull off bangs,

00:05:10.676 --> 00:05:12.077
-because you can't,
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

00:05:12.178 --> 00:05:15.214
you absolutely can't,
believe me I couldn't,

00:05:15.314 --> 00:05:16.415
just learn--

00:05:16.515 --> 00:05:18.450
